[[[break]]]deleted at line 15: *red {code *Redirecting an IoWiki address to the wider web*

If a page {source some.page} begins with "redirect://http://some.page" then IoWiki will ask the client web browser to redirect to "http://some.page" ... unless the request was for {source some.page?action=edit}, in which case IoWiki will present the page for editing in the normal way.

