Mon Nov 14 00:08:35 EST 2005



[[[break]]]deleted at line 27: *red {code *Loading All Pages Into Memory*

I don't really think this feature is useful, but I felt like making a way to load all the pages into the memory cache: go to
http://your.site:8080/cache?action=fillCache.  Otherwise, pages are loaded into the memory cache when each one is requested.

}*
